events.name: July 2019 Quest Run
events.description:
Hello, Indore!

NOTE: REGISTER HERE https://forms.gle/86gmuJzbRfdmCUUr7

events.description:

Unlike our other events, cloud summit is strictly invitation only. Cloud Community Day is meant to bring together professionals working on cloud in an environment where they can learn, network and most importantly: Interact with special Developer Advocates coming all the way from San Francisco!

After the event is over, those who are interested can join us for a lazy stroll down Sarafa Bazaar!

organizers.name: Google Cloud Developer C.
organizers.bio:
Google Cloud Developers Community(GCDC) Indore is an open community backed by Google.
GCDC started with a vision to conduct meetups that mainly deals with Cloud technologies on Google Cloud Platforms.
